  Locus:
    Page: 446
    Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Spirituality
---
Spiritually, man is a giant. Spiritually, there is nothing impossible for
man to accomplish. Godman never becomes defeated. Therefore, keep the
mental soil well-tilled and your harvest shall be great.
